trans-unit.source: Specifies that this object supports a simple, transacted notification for batch initialization.
trans-unit.target: Angir at dette objektet støtter en enkel og utført varsling for satsvis initialisering.

trans-unit.source: ISupportInitialize allows controls to optimize multiple property assignments.
trans-unit.target: ISupportInitialize tillater kontroller til å optimalisere flere egenskapen tildelinger.

trans-unit.source: As a result, you can initialize co-dependent properties or batch set multiple properties at design time.
trans-unit.target: Resultatet du kan starte avhengige av andre egenskaper eller bunke angi flere egenskaper på utformingstidspunktet.

trans-unit.source: Call the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISupportInitialize.BeginInit%2A> method to signal the object that initialization is starting.
trans-unit.target: Kall den <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISupportInitialize.BeginInit%2A>metoden signalisere objektet som initialisering starter.</xref:System.ComponentModel.ISupportInitialize.BeginInit%2A>

trans-unit.source: Call the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISupportInitialize.EndInit%2A> method to signal that initialization is complete.
trans-unit.target: Kall den <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISupportInitialize.EndInit%2A>metoden signalisere at initialiseringen er fullført.</xref:System.ComponentModel.ISupportInitialize.EndInit%2A>

trans-unit.source: Signals the object that initialization is starting.
Signals the object that initialization is complete.
trans-unit.target: Signaliserer objektet som initialiseringen er fullført.
